 eV. This\nwork illustrates that environmental proximity engineering provides a robust\nmethod to indirectly manipulate the band profile of 2D materials outside the\nlimits of their intrinsic properties, providing avenues for future device\ndesign.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Aug 2022 04:18:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-10"}
