ith just one\ndriving mechanism, which was impossible to accomplish with the Aristotelian\ntheory of homocentric spheres.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Aug 2022 14:51:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 14 Aug 2022 13:01:58 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2022 13:28:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-31"}
